# Per-run artifacts
.auth/
node_modules/
# WebKit may drop `core` dumps here on crash — never commit (multi-GB).
core
tests/
# Visual regression: committed baselines live at visual-snapshots/
# but Playwright writes a `*-actual.png` and `*-diff.png` next to them
# on failure — don't commit those.
**/*-actual.png
**/*-diff.png
